      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for exceptional throttle response. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a precise Getrag six-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis remains rigid with verified subframe integrity, while the suspension retains its communicative MacPherson strut and multi-link geometry. Recent maintenance includes a valve clearance adjustment and cooling system refresh. While the finish shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical vitals are robust, making this a technically sound specimen for the spirited enthusiast.",
